item.title: Re:Kindle Love
item.description:
Tue 30 Nov1999 - In Mandarin with English surtitles. Dinner and a musical combine in this package for the Valentine weekend. The production stars Emma Yong, a veteran performer who has appeared in more than 60 lead roles in Singapore, and chronicles the plight of a young man and his relationships with three women from different generations. 5-7 & 9-11 Feb; 7.30pm. $48; 12-14 Feb; 7pm (dinner package). $150 per person or
$250 per couple, inclusive of festive dinner and door gift.
